data.text: Timișoara is the capital city of Timiș County, and the main social, economic, transport, cultural and educational centre in western Romania. One of the largest Romanian cities, Timișoara is the informal capital city of the historical region of Banat. It is also often described as the most cosmopolitan city in Romania.
